sing price on", "bbox": [162.5, 737.5, 1112.5, 758.3]}, {"text": "either the first day of the offering period or the last day of the purchase period, whichever was lower. Under the", "bbox": [162.5, 762.5, 1112.4, 783.3]}, {"text": "ESPP, the offering and purchase periods took place concurrently in consecutive six month increments. Therefore,", "bbox": [162.5, 787.5, 1112.3, 808.3]}, {"text": "the look-back for determining the purchase price was six months. Employees could invest up to 15% of their", "bbox": [162.5, 812.5, 1112.4, 833.3]}, {"text": "gross compensation through payroll deductions. In no event was an employee permitted to purchase more than", "bbox": [162.5, 837.5, 1112.4, 858.3]}, {"text": "8,334 shares of common stock during any six-month purchase period.", "bbox": [162.5, 862.5, 744.8, 883.3]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2011, there were 2,785,721 shares available for future issuance under the 2002", "bbox": [204.2, 906.7, 1112.5, 927.5]}, {"text": "Employee Stock Purchase Plan. The Company’s ESPP was suspended in 2011 and there were no offerings in", "bbox": [162.5, 931.7, 1112.5, 952.5]}, {"text": "2011.", "bbox": [162.5, 956.7, 209.4, 977.5]}, {"text": "During the years ended December 31, 2010 and 2009, employees purchased approximately 46,112 and", "bbox": [204.2, 1000.8, 1112.5, 1021.7]}, {"text": "224,799 shares at average prices of $58.41 and $25.65 per share, respectively. Cash received from purchases", "bbox": [162.5, 1025.8, 1112.4, 1046.7]}, {"text": "under the ESPP for the years ended December 31, 2010 and 2009 was $2.7 million and $5.8 million,", "bbox": [162.5, 1050.8, 1112.3, 1071.7]}, {"text": "respectively.", "bbox": [162.5, 1075.8, 268.4, 1096.7]}, {"text": "Stock-Based Compensation", "bbox": [162.5, 1129.5, 398.1, 1150.3]}, {"text": "Vested stock options granted before June 30, 2004 can be exercised up to three months following", "bbox": [204.2, 1164.3, 1112.4, 1185.1]}, {"text": "termination of employment. Vested stock options granted after June 30, 2004 and before January 1, 2007 can be", "bbox": [162.5, 1189.3, 1112.5, 1210.1]}, {"text": "exercised up to one year following termination of employment. Vested stock options granted after January 2007", "bbox": [162.5, 1214.3, 1112.5, 1235.1]}, {"text": "will remain exercisable for the full ten year contractual term regardless of employment status. The following", "bbox": [162.5, 1239.3, 1112.4, 1260.1]}, {"text": "table summarizes the assumptions used to value option grants using the lattice-binomial model:", "bbox": [162.5, 1264.3, 959.2, 1285.1]}, {"text": "Year Ended December 31,", "bbox": [711.6, 1303.1, 898.6, 1319.8]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [628.6, 1328.1, 662.0, 1344.8]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [788.4, 1328.1, 821.8, 1344.8]}, {"text": "2009", "bbox": [948.2, 1328.1, 981.6, 1344.8]}, {"text": "Dividend yield . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [245.8, 1358.4, 549.8, 1379.3]}, {"text": "0%", "bbox": [681.8, 1358.4, 709.5, 1379.3]}, {"text": "0%", "bbox": [841.6, 1358.4, 869.3, 1379.3]}, {"text": "0%", "bbox": [1001.4, 1358.4, 1029.1, 1379.3]}, {"text": "Expected volatility . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [245.8, 1383.4, 549.8, 1404.3]}, {"text": "51% – 65%", "bbox": [612.3, 1383.4, 709.5, 1404.3]}, {"text": "46% – 54%", "bbox": [772.1, 1383.4, 869.3, 1404.3]}, {"text": "46% – 56%", "bbox": [931.9, 1383.4, 1029.1, 1404.3]}, {"text": "Risk-free interest rate . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [245.8, 1408.4, 549.8, 1429.3]}, {"text": "2.05% – 3.42%", "bbox": [581.0, 1408.4, 709.5, 1429.3]}, {"text": "2.65% – 3.67%", "bbox": [740.8, 1408.4, 869.3, 1429.3]}, {"text": "2.60% – 3.62%", "bbox": [900.6, 1408.4, 1029.1, 1429.3]}, {"text": "Suboptimal exercise factor . . . . . . .", "bbox": [245.8, 1433.4, 549.8, 1454.3]}, {"text": "2.17 – 3.64", "bbox": [615.8, 1433.4, 709.6, 1454.3]}, {"text": "1.78 – 3.28", "bbox": [775.6, 1433.4, 869.4, 1454.3]}, {"text": "1.73 – 2.01", "bbox": [935.4, 1433.4, 1029.2, 1454.3]}, {"text": "67", 